{"tid":2249387,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男文員涉去年10.1拒捕傷警 甩指甲警長：食得鹹魚抵得渴 當差預咗","createTime":"2020-10-19T10:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T12:15:40.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"36afdd7f47350c1b1de6cc553cd6bba511c1c0bd","tid":2249387,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:00:27.000Z","msg":"去年10.1中國國慶當日，各區均有示威衝突。一名男文員被指在屯門看見警車後轉身跑走，警長追逐並將他按在地上，搜出士巴拿等工具。警長其後發現拇指指甲脫落，相信是與文員糾纏期間造成。涉案文員被控一項拒捕罪，今在屯門裁判法院受審。辯方盤問稱被告當時根本無掙扎，警長當時亦未有以襲擊罪名拘捕他；只因警長得悉被告有傷痕，為免「有手尾跟」，才創造出被告掙扎的說法。警長否認，更稱：「食得鹹魚抵得渴！當得差，預咗。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/IJNLBYQJ4BCDRLT7DKD5O7KPNU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FIJNLBYQJ4BCDRLT7DKD5O7KPNU%2F&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZonGVh3W70%2FpCcVRRx8QUyg%3D&h=dcb0c9ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FIJNLBYQJ4BCDRLT7DKD5O7KPNU%2F&h=63ac5690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/IJNLBYQJ4BCDRLT7DKD5O7KPNU/</a>"},{"pid":"3d3f9608b1d286e3b94d3292e75fedf47ae89b83","tid":2249387,"uid":18503,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:01:38.000Z","msg":"預埋死全家"},{"pid":"7b8fd65dbfb3e213a415189ddcde96a35950deb9","tid":2249387,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:05:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f158dd04192db60cede5d8dea2c8865f3d4c104","tid":2249387,"uid":345502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36afdd7f47350c1b1de6cc553cd6bba511c1c0bd","tid":2249387,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:00:27.000Z","msg":"去年10.1中國國慶當日，各區均有示威衝突。一名男文員被指在屯門看見警車後轉身跑走，警長追逐並將他按在地上，